_Scary Azeri_ recounts some personal stories of how people in Azerbaijan love
to spread gossip. Also true for the other two countries making up the region,
and especially Armenia, [such an intrusion into the private lives of others is
particularly relished when it comes to presumed relationships between men and
women regardless of whether such gossip is true or
not](http://scaryazeri.blogspot.com/2010/08/well-i-guess-you-are-sleeping-
with-him.html).

